435\u043d\u0441\u043e\u0440\u044b \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043e\u0431\u043d\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u0434\u0435\u0444\u0435\u043a\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u0441\u0430\u043c\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0442\u043e\u0432 - \u0420\u0418\u0410 \u041d\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0438, 20.02.2019|website=ria-ru.cdn.ampproject.org|access-date=2019-05-02}}</ref>\n\n== Notable professors ==\n\n* [[Igor Tamm]]\n* [[Vladimir Obruchev]]\n* [[Nikolay Mitrofanovich Krylov]]\n* [[Abram Ioffe]]\n* [[Boris Grekov]]\n* [[Vladimir Vernadsky]]\n\n== Review ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n|[[File:Development of new campuses of the Crimean Federal University.jpg|thumb|Development of new campuses of the Crimean Federal University]]\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Simferopol]]\n", "text_old": "{{merge to|Tavrida National V.I. Vernadsky University|discuss=Talk:Tavrida National V.I. Vernadsky University#Proposed merge with V.I. Vernadsky Crimean Federal University|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox university\n|name = V.I. Vernadsky Crimean Federal University\n|native_name = \u041a\u0440\u044b\u043c\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0444\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0443\u043d\u0438\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0438\u0442\u0435\u0442 \u0438\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0438 \u0412.\u0418. \u0412\u0435\u0440\u043d\u0430\u0434\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e\n|image_name = \n|image_size = 200px\n|motto = ''Nosce te ipsum'' ([[Latin]])\n|mottoeng = Know thyself\n|established = 1918\n|type = [[Federal university]]\n|rector = Andrei Falaleev\n|president = \n|students = 35000\n|academic_staff = \n|campus = \n|colours = \n|address = 4, Academica Vernanskogo Avenue\n|city = [[Simferopol]], [[Crimea]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|44|56|11|N|34|08|03|E|region:UA-43_type:edu|display=inline,title}}\n|country = [[Russia]]/[[Ukraine]]\n|website = http://www.eng.cfuv.ru\n}}\n'''V.I. Vernadsky Crimean Federal University''' is a higher education institution